similar to the late King Hussein: Boris Yeltsin, whose butchery in
Chechnya is rarely mentioned in the West, waved to the cameras _ I
am alive, I am alive, he was trying to tell us _ and walked
falteringly into the palace. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
</P>
<ANNOTATION>
    &UR; (STORY CAN END HERE AT 1,500. 250-WORD OPTIONAL TRIM FOLLOWS) &LR;  &QC; 
</ANNOTATION>
