<HEADLINE>
ACADEMY VOTERS LOVE `SHAKESPEARE,' `RYAN'
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY GLENN WHIPP  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
