</P>
<P>
   Q: I often hear or read of people, including some famous people,
receiving cancer treatments at the Fred Hutchinson Cancer Research
Center in Seattle, but nothing is ever said about the center
itself. Who was Fred Hutchinson?
</P>
<P>
   A: Known among cancer researchers and doctors as ``the Hutch,''
the Fred Hutchinson Cancer Research Center was established in 1975
