</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Spotlight on Edward Norton (`Rounders')
 &HT;    Staff reports
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Primal Fear'' _ Playing a choirboy and murder suspect, with
more than one personality.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``The People vs. Larry Flynt'' _ Defending porn king Flynt
(Woody Harrelson) in Milos Forman's exuberant, funny biopic.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Everyone Says I Love You'' _ Bursting into song in Woody
Allen's peculiar musical.
</P>
