<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    With GEORGE-WASHINGTON. Moving in (w) Washington, (l) lifestyle
and (t) travel categories for release Sunday, Feb. 21.
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   IF YOU GO
</P>
<P>
   Mount Vernon is located near Alexandria, Va., and just across
the Potomac River from Washington, D.C.
</P>
<P>
   It is open every day from 9 a.m. to 4 p.m., with longer hours in
the summer.
</P>
<P>
   Admission is $8 for adults; $7.50 for senior citizens; and $4
for children under age 11 when accompanied by an adult. For
information, call 703-780-2000.
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
