<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CIRCUITS-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Circuits stories from The N.Y. Times News Service for Thursday,
Feb. 11:
</P>
<P>
   CIR-NASCAR (Undated) _ Nascar racers are using computers more
and more to tune their cars, but so far the sport wants to stay
