 Wednesday, Feb. 10, 1999    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service will file the following for Thursday and
Sunday. If you have questions, please call Chuck Lewis or Tim
Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about Houston Chronicle
sports stories, please call the Houston Chronicle Sports
Department, 713-220-7896.
