   (Adds: BUSH-2000; DOOMSDAY-CULT; EDUCATION-TEXAS; JASPER-TRIAL;
FRATERINITY-DEATH; TRASH-FEUD; RAC-DAYTONA; and BKN-ROCKETS.)
