50 stores this year, for example. Galyan's Trading Co. is forging
ahead with its giant retail-entertainment format. Manufacturers
like Nike and Reebok are opening up retail outlets at a fast clip.
And then there's the NBA and NASCAR testing their own retail
outlets. Oversaturation is the biggest problem in the industry.
(Bond, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
