</P>
<P>
   HOME-SALES (Los Angeles) _ The suburban Los Angeles community of
Tarzana was among 10 California cities and communities recording
the biggest annual gain last year in the median housing price,
according to a trade group. Statewide, 1998 turned in a record year
in both sales and prices, said the California Association of
Realtors. By Gregory J. Wilcox.
</P>
