<SLUG> BC-FILM-AFFLICTION-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
(RESENDING TO FIX BYLINE) 
NICK NOLTE'S MASTERY COMMANDS THIS WOEFUL TALE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ELVIS MITCHELL 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Doom seems inevitable in writer//director Paul Schrader's
adaptation of Russell Banks' novel ``Affliction.'' Snowbound, the
