<P>
   IMPEACH-RDP (Washington) _ Developments on impeachment: As the
Senate debates privately for a second straight day on whether to
remove President Clinton from office, two Republicans announce that
they will oppose both articles of impeachment. Sens. James Jeffords
of Vermont and Arlen Specter of Pennsylvania, both party moderates,
say they will not support either the perjury or the obstruction of
