<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-10 21:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9922 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ORE-OIL-SPILL-NYT &LR;      02-10 0819
